---
/**
 * EventDrivenPatterns.astro
 * Event-driven architecture patterns comparison
 */
---

<div class="edp-wrap">
  <h3 class="edp-title">Event-Driven Architecture Patterns</h3>
  <div class="edp-patterns">
    <div class="edp-pattern" style="--i:0; --color:#818cf8;">
      <div class="edp-badge">Event Notification</div>
      <div class="edp-flow">Service A → "Order Created" event → Service B reacts</div>
      <div class="edp-desc">Thin event, just a signal. Consumer fetches full data if needed.</div>
      <div class="edp-pros">Low coupling, small payloads</div>
    </div>
    <div class="edp-pattern" style="--i:1; --color:#06b6d4;">
      <div class="edp-badge">Event-Carried State Transfer</div>
      <div class="edp-flow">Service A → "Order Created" + full order data → Service B caches locally</div>
      <div class="edp-desc">Fat event, carries all data. Consumer never calls back to producer.</div>
      <div class="edp-pros">No runtime dependency, eventual consistency</div>
    </div>
    <div class="edp-pattern" style="--i:2; --color:#f59e0b;">
      <div class="edp-badge">Event Sourcing</div>
      <div class="edp-flow">All changes stored as events → Current state = replay all events</div>
      <div class="edp-desc">Events ARE the source of truth. State is derived, not stored directly.</div>
      <div class="edp-pros">Full audit trail, time travel, replay capability</div>
    </div>
    <div class="edp-pattern" style="--i:3; --color:#4ade80;">
      <div class="edp-badge">CQRS</div>
      <div class="edp-flow">Write model (commands) → Events → Read model (queries)</div>
      <div class="edp-desc">Separate write and read paths optimized independently.</div>
      <div class="edp-pros">Scale reads and writes independently, tailored views</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .edp-wrap{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0f172a,#1e293b);border:1px solid #334155;border-radius:16px;padding:2rem;margin:2rem 0}
  .edp-title{color:#f1f5f9;text-align:center;font-size:1.25rem;margin:0 0 1.5rem}
  .edp-patterns{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:.75rem}
  .edp-pattern{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03);border:1px solid var(--color);border-radius:12px;padding:1.25rem;opacity:0;animation:edpFade .4s ease forwards;animation-delay:calc(var(--i)*.15s)}
  @keyframes edpFade{from{opacity:0;transform:translateX(-12px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateX(0)}}
  .edp-badge{background:var(--color);color:#0f172a;font-size:.65rem;font-weight:700;padding:.15rem .5rem;border-radius:6px;display:inline-block;margin-bottom:.5rem}
  .edp-flow{color:#06b6d4;font-family:monospace;font-size:.75rem;background:rgba(0,0,0,.3);padding:.4rem .7rem;border-radius:6px;margin-bottom:.4rem}
  .edp-desc{color:#94a3b8;font-size:.8rem;margin-bottom:.3rem}
  .edp-pros{color:#4ade80;font-size:.78rem}.edp-pros::before{content:'✓ '}
</style>
